# XORS Brand System

## Logo Assets

SVG logos in `public/brand/logo/`. Use `xors-logo-full.svg` for headers, `xors-logo-symbol.svg` for favicons/marks. Stroke variants have `-stroke` suffix.

## Color Palette

```scss
$charcoal: #4A4A4A;      // dark backgrounds
$gold: #F5B800;           // primary accent
$cyan: #00E8A0;           // secondary accent (use sparingly)
$red: #FF0000;            // tertiary accent (use sparingly)
$black: #0A0A0A;          // text on light, symbol on light
$white: #FAFAFA;          // text on dark, light backgrounds
$surface: #F5F5F5;        // subtle surface distinction
$border-light: #E5E5E5;   // borders on light
$border-dark: #333333;    // borders on dark
$text-secondary: #525252; // muted text on light
$text-muted: #A3A3A3;     // very muted text
```

## Typography

- Body: Inter (400, 500, 600)
- Mono: JetBrains Mono (code/data)
- Headings: normal weight, `letter-spacing: -0.02em`
- Labels: small, uppercase, `letter-spacing: 0.05em`
- Body line-height: 1.6

## Visual Rules

- Zero border-radius throughout
- Sections separated by `border-top: 1px solid` lines
- Generous vertical rhythm (64-96px between sections)
- Max content: 800px for reading, 1200px for layouts
- Buttons: outlined, uppercase, wide tracking, hover inverts fg/bg
- CTAs end with arrows: `→`
- Headlines: lowercase, conversational, confident
- Body: muted color with key terms in foreground color
